    • flags

      default Flag[] flags()
      Gets Flags for this OpenemsApp. A Flag could be anything that would describe the app more.

      Flags may be specific for Monitoring e. g. only show the app after a key was entered (Flags.SHOW_AFTER_KEY_REDEEM).

      Returns:
      an array of Flags
